dictionary.description: Meryl Stryfe and Milly Thompson are agents of the Bernardelli Insurance Society, combing the wasteland to evaluate and report on claims made against Vash the Stampede. While they prefer peaceful solutions to many of their problems, both are experts in concealed weaponry, negotiation tactics, and running to and from danger very quickly. While their encounters with the Humanoid Typhoon were coincidental in the beginning, fate soon conspired to bring them together in their adventures. Originally ordered by their superiors to follow Vash and keep any trouble around him in check—and bring a quick resolution to any problems that came up—the two soon became allies in his fight against the many villains in the outlands. Now, as time passes in the new world, the legends of Derringer Meryl and Stungun Milly begin to grow...
